{
  "stem": "18770.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And a year and a half later, or two years later, I move to Australia and do nothing but teach people how to enhance the quality of their lives.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Where does that come from?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, I mean, that's, that's extraordinary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So-- Well, where do you think that did come from?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I think that has something to do with a bunch of things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think it has to do with both my-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I think it has to do with something in my family past because I think that the-- my grandfather, having been a rabbi, or if he wasn't an official rabbi, he had that quality.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In other words, in family of businessmen, he was like the spiritual anchor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my memory of him as a child, although I hardly knew him, was him sitting there with the Talmud or whatever books, or Rashi, whatever he was looking at, studying, you know, the way Jews rock back and forth.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it made a very definite strong impression on me as a child.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That, I think is one aspect.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I feel that's in my past.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think that's in the Jewish past anyway, to work with enhancing consciousness.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think that's a very deep part of Jewish tradition which sometimes gets lost, you know, where families turn towards the-- towards the business end of life.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For me, it was very strong.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think maybe because of the war, I had been more sensitized to people's suffering, to, to people's dislocations, to people searching for their identities.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think, you know, that plus the unexplainable aspect of it, but I think this has definitely contributed to it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So here I'm in my mid-forties.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I totally change my life.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
